            <p>Larger vans, 4x4 light utility vehicles, motorised horseboxes, pickups (exceeding 1,205kg unladen and not exceeding 3,500kg GVW)</p>
            <p>Ambulances and motorcaravans (2,500kg to 3,500 kg GVW)</p>
