            <p>Lorries, motorised horse boxes, breakdown and recovery vehicles, snow ploughs, gritters, refuse collection vehicles, road sweepers, concrete mixers, fire engines, tippers, removals lorries (exceeding 3,500kg GVW)</p>
            <p>Buses and coaches (more than eight passenger seats, exceeding 5,000kg GVW)</p>
            <strong></strong></td>
